      "message": "doc: clarify tr() descriptor key tweaking and add BIP references\n\nMake explicit that the output key in tr() descriptors is computed by\ntweaking the internal key as defined in BIP 341, and reference BIP 386\nfor the full specification of tr() output descriptors.\n\nCloses #30279",
